  <brief_title>Posterior IVS Versus Sacrospinous Suspension in Vaginal Vault Prolapse Repair</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Evaluation of Morbidity and Efficacy of Posterior IVS (Infracoccygeal Sacropexy), in Comparison to the Standard Sacrospinous Suspension in the Surgical Treatment of Vaginal Vault Prolapse by the Vaginal Route.</official_title>
